 I finish this about 8 in the even A lot of Scottish regiment pass through here this even bound for Albert the Somm , they are fine fellow are the Jock our chap get on famous with them . The boy are get the beer wine alright in spite of all the order forbid it , I am sorri to say that a lot of them are make hog of themselv . A small mail came in this afternoon I got a coupl of letter out of it veri welcom they were too Saw Ferguson again tonight had a good long yarn to him he is a fine fellow , a mate of mine he is one of the old origion
